{"tid":699507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 冷氣技工墮梯命危　傷者與90歲母相依為命","createTime":"2018-06-12T14:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T15:37:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02fe30920cbaefa33703243ef27ccf4bb0d086b3","tid":699507,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/photo/bkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180612212618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180612212618&h=44ff8d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荃灣荃新天地昨晚發生的工人墮梯嚴重意外，姓高(47歲)傷者送往瑪嘉烈醫院急救後，目前情況仍然危殆，留院深切治療部，家人透露，高昨晚曾接受腦部手術，減顱內壓，但仍然偏高，因此在今日下午，又再進一次同樣的手術，希望他情況好轉。<br />\n<br />\n家人表示，高任職冷氣技工已有一段時間，未婚，與90歲母親同住葵涌區，是顧家的孝順仔，上月母親節，他特意帶母親出外用膳慶祝。事發昨晚10時許，高在荃新天地一間髮型屋，進行冷氣維修，期間疑失足從約4米高的人字梯墮下，頭部重傷陷入昏迷，在場工友見狀立即報警。警方將案件列工業意外，勞工處正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fbkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001.html&d=JQD8j6zJUJvgyHEPV5JzaEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=2030fcab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5883717c3f1677a50291fd681acf827ac91ac332","tid":699507,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/photo/bkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180612212618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180612135109345-0612_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180612212618&h=9dc44137&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a768e702a3fea2a2cbd5483da1e293effed19a7b","tid":699507,"uid":131245